Notes: Bradley fifth-year senior guard Gabi Haack broke the program's all-time
scoring record on a 3-pointer with 7:16 left in the 4th quarter for a 53-48
Braves lead. She finished the game with 1,686 career points, surpassing the
previous record of 1,679 points by Karen Anderson from 1979-83.
Game.Officials: Erica Parker, Tim Daley, Doug Knight
